{
  "stem": "10587.6",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Or, if there was a train that would come by, they would run and throw themselves in front of the train or trucks.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So there was a constant-- there was a very morbid type of daily life because-- and-- and that's a place where I was beaten severely because I didn't-- I was so tired because sleep was not enough sleep.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "By the time you got up in the morning, and you cleaned up everything, and you worked an hour-- at least an hour-- to work, and after work-- the building, digging the tunnels-- and the-- and walk-- walk back to the camp, and-- so-- and then you had to clean up the camp, and do whatever they told you to.",
      "word_count": 60
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And this was a very-- probably not much known about this camp.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "It was a horrible camp because this camp also didn't have crematoriums, but it had an open pit where they burned the bodies.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And that was probably the most horrible smell because there was like an open fire.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And at night, they would take commanders.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "They would say you, you, and you, and to take the bodies and carry him there and throw him into the pit.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Many times the SS troopers would take their rifle butts and push you in, and so there were screams.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "People were burned alive, because they would hit him on the head and push him in or stab him, and-- and throw him into the fire.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "So there was always, every night, there was like terrible cries, and yelling, and moaning, and-- and-- and you could really see the fire.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "You know.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, no.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Maybe I wasn't big enough.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Maybe I was lucky that they didn't pick me.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Real tired, yeah, and I was really received some severe beating.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was beaten with a--",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--whip on my rear, but that was already-- that was easy, that was easier.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was beaten up pretty badly, which also took me a while to get over it.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Right, but in-- but in Funfteichen, I was beaten a different way.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was hit with a shovel, and I was hit with the-- with the--",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--with the elbows in my face.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Hersbruck.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Again, right.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Right, and that was-- I was lucky that this was the rear end, because in Hersbruck, they had different kind of methods which I haven't seen in other camp.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They would-- they would take you into the-- the kapos-- they would send the kapos with you to take you to the bathroom, and they would turn on the hose and stick it in your inside and turn it on, so that you, the body, would explode.",
      "word_count": 47
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, in through-- into your mouth and down the-- your trachea.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No one ever survived that.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "This was--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So that was, right, because I was.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I got up real quick, and I got dressed.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And so-- they thought maybe-- and I was also younger-- so they thought maybe I will do some work for a little bit longer, you know, because youth had a lot to do with being alive.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Also, a potluck had also a lot to do with it, because you never knew when you will get hit or with what.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Many time depended where you were at this particular moment for no reason whatsoever, or someone will get ticked off about something, and mainly the SS troopers or the kapos.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The kapos were just as murderous as the SS-- SS troopers.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They carried out a lot of punishments.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So in this camp, we-- I was-- I never-- I never volunteered for anything, but I volunteered always to unload the fruit, and vegetable, and bread and-- for the-- for the SS kitchen, you know.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I was the youngest, and the smallest.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I used to get under the truck and dig a hole and put the food in.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And maybe recover it the next day.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But after a few times, I realized it's a lost cause because the-- the animals found it first at night.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So in-- in this camp, we were not that long because from-- from Hersbruck, we went on another death march, which was a severe death march-- really very bad because it was during winter time.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And in Bavaria, it's-- it's very, very cold.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So we-- we were taken on a march.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And from there we marched to Dachau.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The-- it was very cold, and it was very limited amount of food-- also a lot of people-- the same thing.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They would fall out, fall, and they would be shot, same-- same kind of a routine as from Gross-Rosen, from Funfteichen to Gross-Rosen, one bullet in the head.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We lost a lot of people.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
